            <title>PS5 手掣劈开两半自制「PS Portal」【有片睇】中国网红：价钱便宜一半</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/04/psp/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=psp</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/04/psp/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:56:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS Portal]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手掣]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208505</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 最近推出全新 PS Portal 装置，在这部设计有点像 PS5 手掣劈开两半再加个荧幕的主机上，远端游玩家中的 PS5。由于 PS Portal 手掣仅支援串流 PS5 游戏，却索价 199 美元（约 HK1,555）令不少人却步。然而有中国科技 KOL 在 ChatGPT 的协助下，以半价制作出一部功能与 PS Portal 相近的游戏装置。</p><p>中国影片制作者「贪玩歌姬小宁子」近日于 Bilibili 平台上载一条名为「SONY 卖 199 美元的 PSP，自己做，居然只花了 $$$」的影片。小宁子表示自己没有电子工程基础，在 ChatGPT 的协助及多次的尝试和错误下，最终以 3 个月自家制出 PS Portal 手掣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25.png"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25-694x346.png" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25-694x346.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25-1280x639.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25-768x383.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25-1536x766.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.38.25.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>小宁子首先将 DualSense 及电路板用电锯切成两半，并重新设计一个分开的 PCB 电路板。在手掣部分，小宁子将网上买的 DualSense 手掣外壳，再从边缘慢慢切割，把不必要的给拆解掉，便能制作出两边分开的摇杆。手掣晶片方面，小宁子选用支援蓝牙的 ESP32 晶片，使其自制的手把甚至比 Sony 的多出蓝牙功能。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-1280x716.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-768x430.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-1536x859.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-19.04.47-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.41.23.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.47.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.40.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕截图-2023-12-04-09.42.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在研究电路板时，小宁子称所有问题皆交由 ChatGPT 解决，而大部分的程式也是由 ChatGPT 编写。小宁子只需向 ChatGPT 详细描述问题及要求，并检查其回应，一旦有错便叫 ChatGPT 更改，因此要知道每个程式码的作用。最终将画好的电路图交由任职工程师的母亲审阅其可行性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/1701493498-4ce8fa5ad670d20fc565736f6534a8f0.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/1701493498-4ce8fa5ad670d20fc565736f6534a8f0-694x356.png" alt="" width="694" height="356" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023